snippet.textDisplay:
Another hopeless hack from Jaguar Land Rover. £86k is ridiculous! Range Rover Vogue is the only Range Rover. These smaller suv they are chucking out don’t sell very well at all.
Don’t get me wrong the Velar is smart but for £86k you can buy a Vogue which is heaps nicer. The Evoque was a hit, the sport was a hit, the Vogue was a hit.
Velar is a miss and so will be the new Defender.
These things will be the final nail in the already dirt covered coffin of JLR.
I would hate to be the poor soul that has to try and sell these things in the next year or so. The pressure from management will be intense.
